  "content": "   <p>The agent is both the builder and the first user. If it can't observe the system, it's debugging with println.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"flex-grow\"></div>\n  <div class=\"author-tag\">Lim Chun Zhe</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-number\">02 / 08</div>\n</div>\n<!-- SLIDE 3: OBSERVABILITY — WHAT WE BUILT -->\n<div class=\"slide\">\n  <div class=\"slide-label\">Step 1: Observability</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-title\">\n    OTEL Traces<br>\n    <span class=\"highlight-cyan\">Across Every Operation</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"slide-subtitle\" style=\"font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 28px;\">\n    30 span constants across 7 subsystems. Every kernel operation<br>\n    instrumented at design time. Not bolted on after something broke.\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"terminal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n    <div style=\"color: var(--accent-cyan); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;\">// corvia-telemetry span contracts</div>\n    <div><span style=\"color: var(--accent-purple);\">pub const</span> <span style=\"color: var(--accent-green);\">RAG_CONTEXT</span>: &amp;str = <span style=\"color: var(--accent-amber);\">\"corvia.rag.context\"</span>;</div>\n    <div><span style=\"color: var(--accent-purple);\">pub const</span> <span style=\"color: var(--accent-green);\">ENTRY_EMBED</span>: &amp;str = <span style=\"color: var(--accent-amber);\">\"corvia.entry.embed\"</span>;</div>\n    <div><span style=\"color: var(--accent-purple);\">pub const</span> <span style=\"color: var(--accent-green);\">STORE_SEARCH</span>: &amp;str = <span style=\"color: var(--accent-amber);\">\"corvia.store.search\"</span>;</div>\n    <div><span style=\"color: var(--accent-purple);\">pub const</span> <span style=\"color: var(--accent-green);\">MERGE_PROCESS</span>: &amp;str = <span style=\"color: var(--accent-amber);\">\"corvia.merge.process\"</span>;</div>\n    <div><span style=\"color: var(--accent-purple);\">pub const</span> <span style=\"color: var(--accent-green);\">GC_RUN</span>: &amp;str = <span style=\"color: var(--accent-amber);\">\"corvia.gc.run\"</span>;</div>\n    <div style=\"color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 8px;\">// ... 25 more across agent, session, inference, hooks</div>\n  </div>",
